<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Safe Learning Publication</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
background:#f4f4f4;
color:#333;
transition:0.3s;
}

header{
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#4facfe,#00f2fe);
padding:15px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
color:white;
position:sticky;
top:0;
}

nav a{
color:white;
margin:0 10px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

nav a:hover{
text-decoration:underline;
}

.hero{
height:70vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(120deg,#84fab0,#8fd3f4);
color:#222;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:40px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

section{
padding:50px 20px;
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
}

.cards{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-5px);
}

.quote{
background:#fff;
padding:20px;
border-left:5px solid #4facfe;
}

footer{
background:#222;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:15px;
}

button{
padding:8px 15px;
border:none;
background:#222;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
border-radius:5px;
}

.dark{
background:#121212;
color:white;
}

.dark .card{
background:#1f1f1f;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>

<h2>Safe Learning Publication</h2>

<nav>
<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#books">Books</a>
<a href="#quotes">Quotes</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<button onclick="toggleDark()">Dark Mode</button>

</header>


<section class="hero" id="home">

<h1>Welcome to Safe Learning Publication</h1>

<p>Empowering minds with free knowledge.</p>

<p>Author: Pankaj Sahu</p>

</section>


<section id="about">

<h2>About</h2>

<p>
Safe Learning Publication is a free knowledge platform created by
<b>Pankaj Sahu</b>.
Our mission is to provide educational resources, motivational thoughts,
and digital books for students and learners.
</p>

</section>


<section id="books">

<h2>Books</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>Science Book</h3>
<p>Download free science notes.</p>
<a href="#">Download PDF</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Biology Notes</h3>
<p>Useful notes for students.</p>
<a href="#">Download PDF</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Motivation Guide</h3>
<p>Self improvement ebook.</p>
<a href="#">Download PDF</a>
</div>

</div>

</section>


<section id="quotes">

<h2>Motivational Quotes</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="quote">
Knowledge is the most powerful weapon.
</div>

<div class="quote">
Learning today leads to success tomorrow.
</div>

<div class="quote">
Education is the key to freedom.
</div>

</div>

</section>


<section id="contact">

<h2>Contact</h2>

<p>Email: example@email.com</p>

<p>Instagram: @pankajsahu155</p>

</section>


<footer>

© Safe Learning Publication | Author: Pankaj Sahu

</footer>


<script>

function toggleDark(){
document.body.classList.toggle("dark");
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
